{"tid":1047263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日瓜左果個巴士佬，佢老婆九成九係新移民！","createTime":"2019-03-04T23:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T08:01:27.000Z","uid":202464,"like":38,"dislike":225,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4a526c9009d9a87a9b5f0b1074f01e328bf51079","tid":1047263,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:54:58.000Z","msg":"西九龍走廊今晨發生奪命車禍，城巴59歲車長蘇國偉當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，入職20年的蘇國偉，與妻子育有三子女，長女僅小六（12），二子是小四生（10）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個巴士佬47歲先生第一個。呢種職業，肯嫁畀佢既9成9都係支那人！"},{"pid":"7414be843676d9beedb873f8e19236aa317f9628","tid":1047263,"uid":54791,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b7cbc83b4f4c51519d3bfa61d14f1a99cd2b1a","tid":1047263,"uid":133601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484fea09f83ca553d38e2560fc03653014c43992","tid":1047263,"uid":202464,"like":124,"dislike":9,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:59:42.000Z","msg":"佢老婆帶住三個仔女<br />\n<br />\n先拎巴士佬既恩恤金、保險<br />\n<br />\n然後申請綜援、公屋、書薄津貼<br />\n<br />\n然後改嫁同鄉支那人<br />\n<br />\n然後又落黎團聚<br />\n<br />\n綜援人數加名<br />\n<br />\n新老公分分鐘係支那有幾個支那仔女<br />\n<br />\n然後又落黎團聚<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n發發啦！十個八個咬綜援！"},{"pid":"ed62bc41ed234c17912fdaaa9472ca4908045c58","tid":1047263,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:08:51.000Z","msg":"有講老婆幾歲？"},{"pid":"c1320a77063816e3203bc93bc283d3088dca551e","tid":1047263,"uid":202464,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有講老婆幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n二仔小四10歲。仲有個細仔/女，我當佢8歲。<br />\n<br />\n咁既家底，邊有咁多錢做高齡產婦。多數都係細個巴士佬十幾二十年果種"},{"pid":"91112c59b2001e1194d8825baba51fae7aad6dc9","tid":1047263,"uid":130901,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pi